snippet.title: Tacoma Gameplay Trailer at E3 2015 - Tacoma Trailer
snippet.description:
Tacoma Gameplay Trailer: Tacoma is the new game from the creators of Gone Home, set on Lunar Transfer Station Tacoma where, 200,000 miles from Earth, you must uncover the mysteries of the station and its crew. Subscribe for more on Tacoma and Xbox at E3 2015: http://www.tinyurl.com/SubToOxbox
